cs.IT, cs.NI, cs.COMM, cs.SY, cs.DC 

The paper discusses interference mitigation techniques in multibeam satellite communications, which involves signal processing and communication technologies. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.IT (Information Theory), followed by cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) and cs.COMM (Computer Communications and Networks). The paper also discusses practical challenges and future configurations, which could fall under cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing).
